 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;">于是，</span>酒店老板谢先生之后向他们的单位举报了情况，而各单位分别给予了相应的处罚，陈某被<span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(240, 65, 66); ; ">批评教育还做了书面检查</span></span>，常某则是给<span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(240, 65, 66); ; ">予党内警告处分</span></span>，李某多次上门给老板道歉，最终也受到了<span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(240, 65, 66); ; ">诫勉谈话</span></span>的处罚。</p><p data-track="18" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;">由于始终讨不到一个公道，谢先生无奈之下选择把整件事发在网上，希望能够让大家来判断是非对错。</span></p><p data-track="19" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>4月11日，被打酒店老板谢先生表示，<span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;">自己不服该决定，正在申请行政复议。</span></p><p data-track="20" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>公职人员知法犯法，仗着自己的身份和地位对老百姓进行威胁恐吓，最终也只是党内警告处分，这样的结果显然是很难让大家满意的，如果犯罪成本如此的低，让大家如何继续相信他们！</p><p data-track="21" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 2em;'><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(240, 65, 66); ; ">事情发酵后，不仅酒店老板不服，一生要强的网友们更是不服，评论区吵翻了天。</span></p><p data-track="22" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>网友：处罚还是太轻了，记不住教训。都这么狂了，为何不直接开除公职，果然编制就是护身符。</p><p data-track="23" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>仅仅党内警告，这样看来，这个公务员说的确实是真话，他在福州是真的狂，没人敢跟他对着干。</p><p><img data-imgfileid="100062758" data-ratio="0.46567717996289426" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKBicsBIicWest5OMew49cPqxXUFkryhKHnpgpxVknVysu0rayXvXCNwghQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="1078" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: auto;cursor: zoom-in;display: block;border-radius: 4px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><br></p><p data-track="24" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="font-weight: 700;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;background-color: rgb(252, 241, 184); ; ">网友的评论:</span><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(240, 65, 66); ; "><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;background-color: rgb(252, 241, 184); ; ">开除一个公职人员比研发光刻机还难！</span></span><span style=" border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 209, 209); ; ">要不然怎么叫铁饭碗呢？</span></span></p><p><img data-imgfileid="100062759" data-ratio="1.778391167192429" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKBiaKtuX0REVRBvr8dRXLnChfAiaDQ09NrOibl6nUPM6nubGLsrPJg21hXw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1268" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: auto;cursor: zoom-in;display: block;border-radius: 4px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><br></p><p data-track="25" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>朋友的评论永远是最经典的，也是最精彩的。</p><p data-track="26" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>派出所什么级别，能够处理副市长级别的干部？</p><p data-track="27" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>也有网友担心，这个老板不能在当地混了，要换老板了！</p><p data-track="28" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>还有网友表示，像这样的人员，怎么指望他们办事呢？</p><p><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-imgfileid="100062757" data-ratio="1.1796296296296296" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/hwKD0rwdNo9opMdEgQarfJ4QibgDeMRKB4DI3GMhRfYOmfI7xIW2IGFj08MibuxlfOGKfRzXUZpCgjmmw2l4cdLg/640?wx_fmt=other&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="other" data-w="1080" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: auto;cursor: zoom-in;display: block;border-radius: 4px;"></p><p style="margin-top: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;"><br></p><p data-track="29" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>这次事件再次敲响了警钟，我们必须加强对公职人员的日常管理和监督！</p><p data-track="30" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>首先，从源头上加强公职人员的素质培养。选拔人才时，除了注重专业技能，更要注重品德修养。我们要选拔那些真正有信仰、有担当、有情怀的人才进入公职队伍。</p><p data-track="31" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>其次，建立健全的监管机制。对于公职人员的行为，我们要有严格的规范和监管措施。一旦发现违规行为，必须严惩不贷，绝不姑息。同时，鼓励公众参与监督，让权力在阳光下运行。</p><p data-track="32" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>最后，加强公职人员的自律意识。公职人员要时刻保持清醒的头脑，牢记自己的职责和使命。在面对诱惑和挑战时，要坚守底线，不为私欲所动。</p><p data-track="33" style='margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);font-family: "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>公职人员踹酒店老板两脚的事件令人愤慨，但也为我们提供了反思的机会。让我们共同努力，加强对公职人员的日常管理和监督，为构建和谐社会贡献力量！</p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="134305096" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
